46 SECTION 3.1.
47 (a) The annual salary of the Clerk of the State Court of DeKalb County shall be 90 percent
48 of the annual salary received by the Clerk of the Superior Court of DeKalb County.
49 (b) Each part-time associate judge of the Magistrate Court of DeKalb County shall be paid
50 an hourly rate commensurate with the annual salary provided in this Act to a full-time
51 associate judge of the Magistrate Court of DeKalb County."
52 SECTION 4.
53 Said Act is further amended by adding a new section to read as follows:
54 "SECTION 3.2.
55 Each judge of the State Court, Magistrate Court, Probate Court, or Juvenile Court of
56 DeKalb County and each non-judicial official who pursuant to this Act receives any
57 compensation from DeKalb County funds shall also receive from DeKalb County the same
58 fringe benefits provided to all county employees, including but not limited to health
59 insurance, dental insurance, vision insurance, life insurance, flexible benefits, incentives,
