60 and longevity pay. Each judge or official may opt out of any such fringe benefit. Such
61 fringe benefits shall be calculated based upon the total years of service that the judge or
62 official has provided as a judge, official, or employee of DeKalb County and shall be
63 calculated based upon the judge's or official's total compensation from state or DeKalb
64 County funds. Nothing in this section shall be construed to modify or affect any pension
65 or retirement plan."
66 SECTION 5.
67 (a) Except as provided for in subsection (b) of this section, this Act shall become effective
68 on June 1, 2025.
69 (b) Sections 2 and 3 of this Act shall become effective on August 1, 2025.
70 SECTION 6.
71 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
